       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
      ******************************************************************
      *           I D E N T I F I C A T I O N   D I V I S I O N        *
      ******************************************************************
       PROGRAM-ID. COB01100.
      ******************************************************************
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
      ******************************************************************
      *           E N V I R O N M E N T         D I V I S I O N        *
      ******************************************************************
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.
      ******************************************************************
      *                     CONFIGURATION SECTION                      *
      ******************************************************************
       SPECIAL-NAMES. DECIMAL-POINT IS COMMA.
      ******************************************************************
       INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.
      ******************************************************************
      *                      INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION                      *
      ******************************************************************
       FILE-CONTROL.
           SELECT   COF01100-FILE
                    ASSIGN              TO DISK-COF01100
                    ORGANIZATION        IS SEQUENTIAL
                    FILE STATUS         IS VIAW0011-FSTATUS.

      ******************************************************************
       DATA DIVISION.
      ******************************************************************
      *                   D A T A   D I V I S I O N                    *
      ******************************************************************
       FILE SECTION.
      ******************************************************************
      *                          FILE SECTION                          *
      ******************************************************************
       FD  COF01100-FILE.
           COPY COCF1100.

      ******************************************************************
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
      ******************************************************************
      *                    WORKING STORAGE SECTION                     *
      ******************************************************************
      * CONSTANTES
      ******************************************************************
       01  WS-CONSTANTES.
           05 WS-PROGNAME               PIC  X(10) VALUE 'COB01100'.
           05 WS-COCF1100               PIC  X(10) VALUE 'COF01100'.
           05 WS-ARVT0500               PIC  X(10) VALUE 'ARVT3600'.
           05 WS-COVT3600               PIC  X(10) VALUE 'COVT3600'.
           05 WS-COVT5008               PIC  X(10) VALUE 'COVT5008'.
           05 WS-COVT5401               PIC  X(10) VALUE 'COVT5401'.
           05 WS-FACTVENC               PIC  X(10) VALUE 'FACTVENC'.
           05 WS-CTABELA-PAISES         PIC  X(10) VALUE 'AR047'.

      ******************************************************************
      * VARIAVEIS
      ******************************************************************
       01  WS-VARIAVEIS.
           05 WS-DATA-MIN              PIC X(10)  VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-DATA-HOJE             PIC X(10)  VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-CSTATUS1              PIC X(01)  VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-CSTATUS2              PIC X(01)  VALUE SPACES.

      ******************************************************************
      * COPYS
      ******************************************************************
           COPY AQCL0001.
           COPY AQCW0109.
           COPY VIAL0015.
           COPY VIAW0011.
           COPY VIAW0012.
           COPY VIATK001.
           COPY VIATK002.
           COPY COCK0002.
      ******************************************************************
      * DB2
      ******************************************************************
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE SQLCA       END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE ARCD0500    END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD3600    END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD5008    END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD5401    END-EXEC.

           EXEC SQL
                DECLARE CRS_COT50 CURSOR FOR
                SELECT NIDINVOICE
                     , NIDPROJECTO
                     , GCLIENTE
                     , DDATAINSER
                     , DDATAEMISS
                     , DDATAEMIS2
                     , DDATEDUE
                     , CPRAZO
                     , NTOTALAMOUNT
                     , NTAXAMOUNT
                     , GDESCINVOICE
                     , CSTATUS
                     , CUSERID
                     , HTIMEST
                     , GREFINV
                     , DPAG
                     , CMOEDA
                     , NTOTPAG
                  FROM COVT5008_INVOICES
                 WHERE DDATEDUE <= :COCD5008-DDATEDUE
                   AND DPAG      = :COCD5008-DPAG
                   AND CSTATUS  IN ( :WS-CSTATUS1
                                   , :WS-CSTATUS2 )
              ORDER BY GCLIENTE
                     , NIDPROJECTO
                     , NIDINVOICE
           END-EXEC.

      ******************************************************************
       01  FILLER              PIC X(40) VALUE 'FIM DA WORKING-STORAGE'.
      ******************************************************************
       LINKAGE SECTION.
      ******************************************************************
      *                        LINKAGE SECTION                         *
      ******************************************************************
           COPY AQCW0009.
      ******************************************************************
       PROCEDURE DIVISION USING AQCW0009-DATA.
      ******************************************************************
      *              P R O C E D U R E   D I V I S I O N               *
      ******************************************************************
       0000-MAINLINE.
      ******************************************************************
           PERFORM 1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
              THRU 1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
                 THRU 2000-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT
           END-IF.

           PERFORM 3000-FIM-PROGRAMA
              THRU 3000-FIM-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

       0000-MAINLINE-EXIT.
           GOBACK.

      ******************************************************************
       1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA'      TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM AQCP0100-REG-INICIO
                 THRU AQCP0100-REG-INICIO-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM AQCP0100-OBT-DADOS-ARQ
                 THRU AQCP0100-OBT-DADOS-ARQ-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 1100-OPEN-COCF1100
                 THRU 1100-OPEN-COCF1100-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 1200-WRITE-HEADER
                 THRU 1200-WRITE-HEADER-EXIT
           END-IF.

       1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       1100-OPEN-COCF1100.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '1100-OPEN-COCF1100'        TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           OPEN OUTPUT COF01100-FILE.

           PERFORM 9030-FSCHECK
              THRU 9039-FSCHECK-EXIT.

           EVALUATE TRUE
           WHEN FS-OK
                CONTINUE
           WHEN OTHER
                SET  AQCW0009-RCODE-APL     TO TRUE
                MOVE WS-PROGNAME            TO AQCW0100-PGMNAME
                MOVE VIAL0015-CALLER-ID     TO AQCW0100-PARAGRAPH
                MOVE WS-COCF1100            TO AQCW0100-NM-ENTIDADE
                MOVE VIAW0011-FSTATUS       TO AQCW0100-FILE-STATUS
                PERFORM AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG
                   THRU AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG-EXIT
           END-EVALUATE.

       1100-OPEN-COCF1100-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       1200-WRITE-HEADER.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '1200-WRITE-HEADER'         TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

      * Preencher os titulos das colunas da tabela
           STRING 'Pa疄;'                   DELIMITED BY SIZE
                  'Cliente;'                DELIMITED BY SIZE
                  'Projecto;'               DELIMITED BY SIZE
                  'Sequ瘽cia;'              DELIMITED BY SIZE
                  'Refer瘽cia;'             DELIMITED BY SIZE
                  'Data Vencimento;'        DELIMITED BY SIZE
                  'Data Emiss緌;'           DELIMITED BY SIZE
                  'Montante;'               DELIMITED BY SIZE
                  'Moeda'                   DELIMITED BY SIZE
                                            INTO COCF1100-RECORD.

           WRITE COCF1100-RECORD.

           PERFORM 9030-FSCHECK
              THRU 9039-FSCHECK-EXIT.

           EVALUATE TRUE
           WHEN FS-OK
                CONTINUE
           WHEN OTHER
                SET  AQCW0009-RCODE-APL     TO TRUE
                MOVE WS-PROGNAME            TO AQCW0100-PGMNAME
                MOVE VIAL0015-CALLER-ID     TO AQCW0100-PARAGRAPH
                MOVE WS-COCF1100            TO AQCW0100-NM-ENTIDADE
                MOVE VIAW0011-FSTATUS       TO AQCW0100-FILE-STATUS
                PERFORM AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG
                   THRU AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG-EXIT
           END-EVALUATE.

       1200-WRITE-HEADER-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2000-PROC-PROGRAMA.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2000-PROC-PROGRAMA'        TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           PERFORM 2100-OPEN-CURSOR
              THRU 2100-OPEN-CURSOR-EXIT.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2200-FETCH-CURSOR
                 THRU 2200-FETCH-CURSOR-EXIT

              PERFORM 2300-PROC-CURSOR
                 THRU 2300-PROC-CURSOR-EXIT
                      UNTIL NOT DB2-OK
                         OR NOT AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS

              EXEC SQL
                   CLOSE CRS_COT50
              END-EXEC
           END-IF.

       2000-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2100-OPEN-CURSOR.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2100-OPEN-CURSOR'          TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           INITIALIZE DCLCOCD5008.

           MOVE COCK0002-CSTATUS-EMIT       TO WS-CSTATUS1.
           MOVE COCK0002-CSTATUS-PPAG       TO WS-CSTATUS2.
           MOVE VIAK0002-DATA-MINIMA        TO COCD5008-DPAG.
           MOVE ETCL0002-DATA-PROCESSO      TO COCD5008-DDATEDUE.

           EXEC SQL
                OPEN CRS_COT50
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE WS-COVT5008                 TO VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           EVALUATE TRUE
           WHEN DB2-OK
                CONTINUE
           WHEN OTHER
                SET  AQCW0009-RCODE-APL     TO TRUE
                MOVE WS-PROGNAME            TO AQCW0100-PGMNAME
                MOVE VIAL0015-CALLER-ID     TO AQCW0100-PARAGRAPH
                MOVE VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME    TO AQCW0100-NM-ENTIDADE
                MOVE VIAW0012-SQLCODE       TO AQCW0100-SQLCODE
                PERFORM AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG
                   THRU AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG-EXIT
           END-EVALUATE.

       2100-OPEN-CURSOR-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2200-FETCH-CURSOR.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2200-FETCH-CURSOR'         TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           EXEC SQL
                FETCH CRS_COT50
                 INTO :COCD5008-NIDINVOICE
                    , :COCD5008-NIDPROJECTO
                    , :COCD5008-GCLIENTE
                    , :COCD5008-DDATAINSER
                    , :COCD5008-DDATAEMISS
                    , :COCD5008-DDATAEMIS2
                    , :COCD5008-DDATEDUE
                    , :COCD5008-CPRAZO
                    , :COCD5008-NTOTALAMOUNT
                    , :COCD5008-NTAXAMOUNT
                    , :COCD5008-GDESCINVOICE
                    , :COCD5008-CSTATUS
                    , :COCD5008-CUSERID
                    , :COCD5008-HTIMEST
                    , :COCD5008-GREFINV
                    , :COCD5008-DPAG
                    , :COCD5008-CMOEDA
                    , :COCD5008-NTOTPAG
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE WS-COVT5008                 TO VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           EVALUATE TRUE
           WHEN DB2-OK
           WHEN DB2-NOTFND
                CONTINUE
           WHEN OTHER
                SET  AQCW0009-RCODE-APL     TO TRUE
                MOVE WS-PROGNAME            TO AQCW0100-PGMNAME
                MOVE VIAL0015-CALLER-ID     TO AQCW0100-PARAGRAPH
                MOVE VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME    TO AQCW0100-NM-ENTIDADE
                MOVE VIAW0012-SQLCODE       TO AQCW0100-SQLCODE
                PERFORM AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG
                   THRU AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG-EXIT
           END-EVALUATE.

       2200-FETCH-CURSOR-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2300-PROC-CURSOR.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2300-PROC-CURSOR'          TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           INITIALIZE                          COCF1100-RECORD.
           MOVE ALL ';'                     TO COCF1100-RECORD.

      * Vai formatando o ficheiro output
      * com os campos que obtem das tabelas
           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2400-OBTER-PROJECTO
                 THRU 2400-OBTER-PROJECTO-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2500-OBTER-PAIS
                 THRU 2500-OBTER-PAIS-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2600-OBTER-CLIENTE
                 THRU 2600-OBTER-CLIENTE-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
              IF COCD5401-IVIA = 'S'
                CONTINUE
              ELSE
                PERFORM 2700-WRITE-COCF1100
                   THRU 2700-WRITE-COCF1100-EXIT
              END-IF
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2200-FETCH-CURSOR
                 THRU 2200-FETCH-CURSOR-EXIT
           END-IF.

       2300-PROC-CURSOR-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2400-OBTER-PROJECTO.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2400-OBTER-PROJECTO'       TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           EXEC SQL
                SELECT  CPROJECT
                     ,  PAIS
                  INTO :COCD3600-CPROJECT
                     , :COCD3600-PAIS
                  FROM  COVT3600_PROJECTS
                 WHERE  NIDPROJECTO = :COCD5008-NIDPROJECTO
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE WS-COVT3600                 TO VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           EVALUATE TRUE
           WHEN DB2-OK
                MOVE COCD5008-NIDPROJECTO   TO COCF1100-PROJECT-COD
                MOVE ' - '                  TO COCF1100-PROJECT-SEP
                MOVE COCD3600-CPROJECT      TO COCF1100-PROJECT-DES
                IF COCD3600-CPROJECT (81:) NOT EQUAL SPACES
                   MOVE '...'
                     TO COCF1100-PROJECT-DES(78:)
                END-IF
           WHEN DB2-NOTFND
                MOVE COCD5008-NIDPROJECTO   TO COCF1100-PROJECT-COD
                MOVE SPACES                 TO COCF1100-PROJECT-SEP
                MOVE SPACES                 TO COCF1100-PROJECT-DES
           WHEN OTHER
                SET  AQCW0009-RCODE-APL     TO TRUE
                MOVE WS-PROGNAME            TO AQCW0100-PGMNAME
                MOVE VIAL0015-CALLER-ID     TO AQCW0100-PARAGRAPH
                MOVE VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME    TO AQCW0100-NM-ENTIDADE
                MOVE VIAW0012-SQLCODE       TO AQCW0100-SQLCODE
                PERFORM AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG
                   THRU AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG-EXIT
           END-EVALUATE.

       2400-OBTER-PROJECTO-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2500-OBTER-PAIS.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2500-OBTER-PAIS'           TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE WS-CTABELA-PAISES           TO ARCD0500-CTABELA.
           MOVE COCD3600-PAIS               TO ARCD0500-CCOD.
           MOVE VIATK002-IDIOMA-DFT         TO ARCD0500-CLINGUA.

           EXEC SQL
                SELECT  GDESC
                  INTO :ARCD0500-GDESC
                  FROM  ARVT0500_CODESTABLE
                 WHERE  CTABELA = :ARCD0500-CTABELA
                   AND  CCOD    = :ARCD0500-CCOD
                   AND  CLINGUA = :ARCD0500-CLINGUA
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE WS-ARVT0500                 TO VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           EVALUATE TRUE
           WHEN DB2-OK
                MOVE ARCD0500-GDESC         TO COCF1100-GPAIS
           WHEN DB2-NOTFND
                MOVE COCD3600-PAIS          TO COCF1100-GPAIS
           WHEN OTHER
                SET  AQCW0009-RCODE-APL     TO TRUE
                MOVE WS-PROGNAME            TO AQCW0100-PGMNAME
                MOVE VIAL0015-CALLER-ID     TO AQCW0100-PARAGRAPH
                MOVE VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME    TO AQCW0100-NM-ENTIDADE
                MOVE VIAW0012-SQLCODE       TO AQCW0100-SQLCODE
                PERFORM AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG
                   THRU AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG-EXIT
           END-EVALUATE.

       2500-OBTER-PAIS-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2600-OBTER-CLIENTE.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2600-OBTER-CLIENTE'        TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           EXEC SQL
                SELECT  GNOME,
                        IVIA
                  INTO :COCD5401-GNOME,
                       :COCD5401-IVIA
                  FROM  COVT5401_EMPRESAS
                 WHERE  CSIGLA = :COCD5008-GCLIENTE
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE WS-COVT5401                 TO VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           EVALUATE TRUE
           WHEN DB2-OK
                MOVE COCD5008-GCLIENTE      TO COCF1100-CLIENTE-COD
                MOVE ' - '                  TO COCF1100-CLIENTE-SEP
                MOVE COCD5401-GNOME         TO COCF1100-CLIENTE-DES
           WHEN DB2-NOTFND
                MOVE COCD5008-GCLIENTE      TO COCF1100-CLIENTE-COD
                MOVE SPACES                 TO COCF1100-CLIENTE-SEP
                MOVE SPACES                 TO COCF1100-CLIENTE-DES
           WHEN OTHER
                SET  AQCW0009-RCODE-APL     TO TRUE
                MOVE WS-PROGNAME            TO AQCW0100-PGMNAME
                MOVE VIAL0015-CALLER-ID     TO AQCW0100-PARAGRAPH
                MOVE VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME    TO AQCW0100-NM-ENTIDADE
                MOVE VIAW0012-SQLCODE       TO AQCW0100-SQLCODE
                PERFORM AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG
                   THRU AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG-EXIT
           END-EVALUATE.

       2600-OBTER-CLIENTE-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2700-WRITE-COCF1100.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2700-WRITE-COCF1100'       TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCD5008-NIDINVOICE         TO COCF1100-ZFACTURA.
           MOVE COCD5008-GREFINV            TO COCF1100-GREFERENCIA.
           MOVE COCD5008-DDATEDUE           TO COCF1100-DVENCIMENTO.
           MOVE COCD5008-DDATAEMIS2         TO COCF1100-DEMISSAO.
      *--- Passa a mostrar o montante em divida
      *    MOVE COCD5008-NTOTALAMOUNT       TO COCF1100-MMONTANTE.
           COMPUTE COCF1100-MMONTANTE =
                   COCD5008-NTOTALAMOUNT - COCD5008-NTOTPAG.

           MOVE COCD5008-CMOEDA             TO COCF1100-CMOEDA.

           WRITE COCF1100-RECORD.

           PERFORM 9030-FSCHECK
              THRU 9039-FSCHECK-EXIT.

           EVALUATE TRUE
           WHEN FS-OK
                CONTINUE
           WHEN OTHER
                SET  AQCW0009-RCODE-APL     TO TRUE
                MOVE WS-PROGNAME            TO AQCW0100-PGMNAME
                MOVE VIAL0015-CALLER-ID     TO AQCW0100-PARAGRAPH
                MOVE WS-COCF1100            TO AQCW0100-NM-ENTIDADE
                MOVE VIAW0011-FSTATUS       TO AQCW0100-FILE-STATUS
                PERFORM AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG
                   THRU AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG-EXIT
           END-EVALUATE.

       2700-WRITE-COCF1100-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       3000-FIM-PROGRAMA.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '3000-FIM-PROGRAMA'         TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           CLOSE COF01100-FILE.

      * Processos finais
            PERFORM AQCP0009-TRATA-RCODE
               THRU AQCP0009-TRATA-RCODE-EXIT.

            PERFORM AQCP0002-TRATA-SYNCPOINT
               THRU AQCP0002-TRATA-SYNCPOINT-EXIT.

           PERFORM AQCP0100-REG-FIM
              THRU AQCP0100-REG-FIM-EXIT.

       3000-FIM-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE AQCP0002 END-EXEC.
      ******************************************************************
           COPY AQCP0009.
           COPY AQCP0109.
           COPY VIAP0011.
           COPY VIAP0012.
           COPY VIAP0015.
      ******************************************************************
